---
description: Repo conventions (AGENTS.md is the source of truth)
alwaysApply: true
---

Read **AGENTS.md** — it governs this repo (workflow, hard rules, the gate, DoD).

- Work in your own worktree; **never commit to `main`** (protected — PR + green CI).
- Before claiming success, run: `pnpm run build && pnpm run lint && pnpm run test && pnpm run validate`. Do not invent passing results.
- Smallest correct change; keep diffs small. No new dependencies without asking.
- Reject invalid fill-plans; never auto-"fix" them.
